 |title=Hoyle Scoffs at "Big Bang"
 |url=https://cosmictimes.gsfc.nasa.gov/online_edition/1955Cosmic/hoyle.html
 |publisher=Cosmic Times
 |accessdate=4 September 2017
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214102519/https://cosmictimes.gsfc.nasa.gov/online_edition/1955Cosmic/hoyle.html
 |archive-date=14 December 2016
 |deadurl=no
</ref> but Hoyle explicitly denied this and said it was just a striking image meant to highlight the difference between the two models.<ref>
